          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1593440381656-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, wash the<strong> gem lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with <strong>kitchen paper </strong>and shred</p><p>Combine the <strong>mayo</strong> with the juice of 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1]</span> <strong>lime </strong>in a small bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>lime mayo</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p><p>Dissolve the<strong> tomato paste </strong>and<strong> soy sauce </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1593440402690-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
